# NIX SEARCH
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Search for packages in Nix flakes.
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix search nixpkgs python: Search for 'python' in nixpkgs.

### Essentials
- nix search nixpkgs "python3.*numpy": Search using regex.

### Intermediaries
- nix search . app: Search for packages in the local flake.

### Advanceds
- nix search --json nixpkgs htop: Output results in JSON format for scripting.

## Tips
- Use 'nh search' if available for a faster, more localized experience.

## Disclaimers
- The first search on a large flake (like nixpkgs) can be slow as it indexes.

## Alternatives
- nh search: Modern and faster search utility.

